rows.label: qst201705_msg0001
rows.name:
The Ship-Eating Taos have taken up
residence on this Divine Beast warship.

rows.label: qst201705_msg1001
rows.name:
Please act carefully so as not
to damage the ship itself.

rows.label: qst201705_msg0002
rows.name:
Is this the first time you will have
visited Hadashal Palace, Newt?

rows.label: qst201705_msg0003
rows.name:
It will be fine, as long as you make sure
to behave. And watch your manners
in front of His Majesty!
